titleNullable: Stock prices of Indian Defence companies
subtitleNullable: Top 10 defence companies stock prices listed on NSE/BSE-India.
descriptionNullable:
This dataset is the historical stock prices of the following defense companies listed on NSE and BSE in India:-
0. Bharat Dynamics Limited
1. Hindustan Aeronautics Limited
2. Mazagaon Dock Shipbuilders Limited
3. MTAR Technologies Limited
4. Solar Industries India Limited
5. Astra Microwave Products Limited
6. Bharat Electronics Limited
7. Paras Defence and Space Technologies Limited
8. Bharat Earth Movers Limited
9. Zen Technologies Limited

The stock price is WEEKLY, starting from the listing date of the company on the stock market till 29-01-2023.

Do check out the notebooks related to this dataset. Some work is still in progress on those, so stay tuned.
